    <item>
      <title>联邦快递因成本削减推动业绩好于预期而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/fedex-s-annual-profit-outlook-beats-estimates-on-deep-cost-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦快递公司预计利润将高于华尔街的预期，并表示将在未来一年回购 25 亿美元的股票，有迹象表明其重组和削减成本的全面计划正在实施，这提振了其股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/fedex-s-annual-profit-outlook-beats-estimates-on-deep-cost-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 20:11:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
